#: server.py:203
msgid ""
"\n"
"    该函数是CVE修复流程的第一步，必须严格按照顺序执行：\n"
"        1. 通过调用gitee的api，解析gitee issue URL并获取基本信息\n"
"        2. 将解析得到的issue_info以结构化格式清晰反馈给用户\n"
"        3. 明确告知用户获取到的以下信息：\n"
"           - issue_id: Issue编号\n"
"           - cve_id: CVE编号\n"
"           - org_name: 组织名称\n"
"           - repo_name: 仓库名称\n"
"           - affected_versions: 受影响版本列表\n"
"        4. 解析完成后可自动进入下一步\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    This function is the first step in the CVE remediation process and "
"must be executed strictly in order:\n"
"        1. By calling the Gitee API, parse the Gitee issue URL and obtain"
" basic information\n"
"        2. Clearly feed back the parsed issue_info to the user in a "
"structured format\n"
"        3. Clearly inform the user of the following information obtained:"
"\n"
"           - issue_id: Issue number\n"
"           - cve_id: CVE number\n"
"           - org_name: Organization name\n"
"           - repo_name: Repository name\n"
"           - affected_versions: List of affected versions\n"
"        4. After parsing is completed, automatically proceed to the next "
"step\n"
"    "

