#: server.py:269
msgid ""
"\n"
"    该函数是CVE修复流程的第三步，必须严格按照顺序执行：\n"
"        1. 获取漏洞相关的真实上游提交信息\n"
"        2. 明确反馈以下提交信息：\n"
"           - introduced: 引入漏洞的提交（commit hash和提交信息）\n"
"           - fixed: 修复漏洞的提交（commit hash和提交信息）\n"
"        3. 将获取到的commit信息以清晰格式告知用户\n"
"        4. 获取提交信息完成后可自动进入下一步\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    This function is the third step in the CVE remediation process and "
"must be executed strictly in order:\n"
"        1. Obtain the actual upstream commit information related to the "
"vulnerability\n"
"        2. Clearly report the following commit information:\n"
"           - introduced: The commit that introduced the vulnerability "
"(commit hash and commit message)\n"
"           - fixed: The commit that fixed the vulnerability (commit hash "
"and commit message)\n"
"        3. Inform the user of the obtained commit information in a clear "
"format\n"
"        4. After obtaining commit information is completed, automatically"
" proceed to the next step\n"
"    "

