"        2. 参数说明：\n"
"           - branch: 用户在第四步中选择的分支名（必须从第四步的选择结果中获取）\n"
"           - patch_path: 第四步分析结果中该分支对应的冲突点或补丁路径\n"
"           - clone_dir: 本地克隆目录, 必须与第四步使用的 clone_dir 保持一致\n"
"        3. 执行补丁应用操作：\n"
"           - 切换到指定分支\n"
"           - 应用补丁文件\n"
"           - 若patch应用成功，提交更改\n"
"           - 将修复后的分支推送到fork仓库\n"
"        4. 明确反馈执行结果：\n"
"           - 补丁应用是否成功\n"
"           - 目标分支名称\n"
"           - 修复分支名称（如果创建了新分支）\n"
"           - 应用的补丁路径\n"
"           - 如果失败，明确告知失败原因和解决建议\n"
"        5. 若patch应用失败，提示用户尝试解决冲突后重新执行该步骤\n"
"        6. 对于用户在第四步中选择的每个分支，都需要单独调用此函数执行\n"
"        注意：本地代码位于工作空间里面的仓库名所在的目录\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    This function is the fifth step in the CVE remediation process and "
"must be executed strictly in order (only after the user selects branches "
"in step 4):\n"
"        1. For branches selected by the user in step 4, apply the "
"corresponding patch\n"
"        2. Parameter description:\n"
"           - branch: The branch name selected by the user in step 4 (must"
" be obtained from step 4's selection results)\n"
"           - patch_path: The conflict point or patch path corresponding "
"to this branch in step 4's analysis results\n"
"           - clone_dir: Local clone directory\n"
"        3. Execute patch application operation:\n"
"           - Switch to the specified branch\n"
"           - Apply the patch file\n"
"           - If patch application is successful, commit the changes\n"
"           - Push the fixed branch to the fork repository\n"
"        4. Clearly report the execution results:\n"
"           - Whether the patch application was successful\n"
"           - Target branch name\n"
"           - Fix branch name (if a new branch was created)\n"
"           - Applied patch path\n"
"           - If failed, clearly inform the failure reason and solution "
"suggestions\n"
"        5. If patch application fails, prompt the user to try resolving "
"conflicts and re-execute this step\n"
"        6. For each branch selected by the user in step 4, this function "
"must be called separately\n"
"        Note: Local code is located in the directory named after the "
"repository in the workspace\n"
"    "

